<html lang='en'>
	<head>
		<meta charset='UTF-8' />
		<meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
		<title>Welcome Email</title>
		<style>
			body { background-color: white; color: #1b1464; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
			.container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; } .header { background-color: #1b1464;
			color: white; padding: 10px; text-align: center; } .content, .to-do-list, .core-values { margin-top: 20px; }
			.to-do-list ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; } .to-do-list li { margin-bottom: 10px; } .core-values {
			background-color: #1b1464; color: white; padding: 20px; margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; } .core-values ul {
			list-style: none; padding: 0; } .core-values li { margin-bottom: 10px; } .signature { margin-top: 30px;
			font-style: italic; } @media screen and (max-width: 600px) { .container { width: 95%; padding: 10px; } }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class='container'>
			<div class='header'>
				<h1>Welcome to Three M!</h1>
			</div>
			<div class='content'>
				<p>Hello {{name}},</p>
				<p>We're excited to have you on board as a part of our team at Three M, a leading manufacturing tool and machine
					shop. You are now a key part of a team committed to excellence, innovation, and quality.</p>
				<p>Below, you'll find a to-do list for your first week. These steps are designed to help you get acclimated
					quickly and start your journey with us on the right foot.</p>
			</div>
			<div class='to-do-list'>
				<h2>Your First Week To-Do List</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Complete your employee profile on our internal platform.</li>
					<li>Review the employee handbook and sign the acknowledgment form.</li>
					<li>Schedule a meeting with your team lead to discuss your role and responsibilities.</li>
					<li>Join the introductory training sessions on {{nextTraining}}.</li>
					<li>Set up your workspace and familiarize yourself with the tools and equipment you'll be using.</li>
					<li>Attend the welcome meeting with HR to learn more about company policies and benefits.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class='core-values'>
				<h2>Our Core Values</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Give a Shit</li>
					<li>Be Versatile</li>
					<li>Create Solutions</li>
					<li>Have Fun</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class='signature'>
				<p>Best Regards,</p>
				<p>Three M Team</p>
				<p><small>Please note: This is an automated message from a no-reply system. For assistance, please contact HR or
						your team lead directly.</small></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>